### Vue

#### Format `style[lang="css"]` ([#6875] by [@fisker])

Previously, `<style>` elements with `lang="css"` were not formatted, while omitting the attribute or setting to some other values worked. This oversight has been fixed.

<!-- prettier-ignore -->
```html
<!-- Input -->
